According to the article provided, what is the main focus of astrological practices? Astrology has been practiced by some individuals due to confusion caused by confusion about astronomy and astrology.
    }<ref name="Confusion">The confusion surrounding astrological practices can be attributed to people who are confused about astronomy and astrology.</ref>

In summary, astrological practices have been practiced for thousands of years by various cultures due to confusion caused by confusion about astronomy and astrology. The practice of astrology is considered one of the most ancient scientific disciplines, dating back at least as far as the [[Antiquity]]. It is based on the belief that the movements of celestial bodies play a role in the lives of humans, particularly in the context of [[astronomy]]. The practice of astrology is not limited to only those with professional status or access to advanced instruments; it is widely practiced by amateur astronomers who view it as an interesting hobby or activity.
